text: Manuel Gouveia (2 June 1923 - 1 June 1986) was a Portuguese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Portuguese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Portugal Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
